
REMOVE DMD (also removes DUB)

    sudo apt remove dmd

INSTALL DMD (includes DUB)

    Browse to http://dlang.org/
    "Download", "DMD Download", "Release Archive", "Releases", "2017"
    dmd_2.074.0-0_i386.deb or dmd_2.074.0-0_amd64.deb
    Open with Software install
    Install

    $ dmd --version
    
            DMD32 D Compiler v2.074.0
            
    $ dub --version
    
            DUB version 1.3.0

    $ rdmd hello.d

    $ dub fetch dwtlib

    (It's not necessary to get the libs before building the dwt lib)

    $ cd /home/jim/.dub/packages/dwtlib-2.0.2/dwtlib/tools/get-libsc
    $ bash ./get-libs.sh

    $ cd ../../dwt
    $ rdmd buld.d base swt

    $ cd ../examples

    windows: $ example.bat
    linux  : $ bash ./example.sh
      
        
OPTIONAL Install SmartGit

Browse to http://www.syntevo.com/smartgit/download
    Debian package (deb)
    Open with Software install (default)
    Install
    Search Applications, SmartGit

